                </td>
                <td class="text-primary">
                  {"Ganador P3:"}<span class="font-semibold">Esc. W.A.Mora Samaniego</span>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr class="mb-10 bg-white p-4">
                <td class="py-1 px-0 font-semibold">04:15 P.M. B</td>
                <td class="text-primary">
                  <span class="text-primary">
                    {"Ganador P2:"}
